@TheIdealCard No Contact Networking Cards

@TheIdealCard The Smartest Business Card In The World
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
@TheIdealCard Smart Contactless #DigitalBusinessCards by @INKGILITY
⁣⁣
The Reinvention of the #BusinessCard is Finally Here thanks to @INKGILITY⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
Tap into the Future of #BusinessCards with @TheIdealCard, A Smart #Contactless #DigitalBusinessCard for The Digital Age.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
@TheIdealCard is a chip embedded instrument that triggers an Add to Contacts action on Compatible #Smartphones such as an #iPhone & #Android phone displaying voluminous, just transferred contact details in a matter of seconds.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
You can transfer details such as your Name, Company Name, A Photo or Logo, Email Address, Phone Number(s), Website, Physical Address with directions from Google Maps, Social Media Profiles & Instant Messaging Profiles, Payment Profiles, Emergency Contact Information, Videos, Music, Shopping Pages, an Elevator Pitch, Upcoming Events, and much more.⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
@TheIdealCard comes as a card, ring, key holder, wallet, smartphone sticky, and many more items for added convenience.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
Visit www.TheIdealCard.com to place your order for the only #Networking Card you'll ever need from just $15 ⁣@TheIdealCard⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
Developed by @INKGILITY, The World’s Most Innovative Marketing Company & Largest Selection of #BusinessCards @INKGILITY

node.text:
@TheIdealCard The Smartest Business Card In The World⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
@TheIdealCard Smart Contactless #DigitalBusinessCards by @INKGILITY
⁣⁣
The Reinvention of the #BusinessCard is Finally Here thanks to @INKGILITY⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
Tap into the Future of #BusinessCards with @TheIdealCard, A Smart #Contactless #DigitalBusinessCard for The Digital Age.⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
@TheIdealCard is a chip embedded instrument that triggers an Add to Contacts action on Compatible #Smartphones such as an #iPhone & #Android phone displaying voluminous, just transferred contact details in a matter of seconds.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
You can transfer details such as your Name, Company Name, A Photo or Logo, Email Address, Phone Number(s), Website, Physical Address with directions from Google Maps, Social Media Profiles & Instant Messaging Profiles, Payment Profiles, Emergency Contact Information, Videos, Music, Shopping Pages, an Elevator Pitch, Upcoming Events, and much more.⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
@TheIdealCard comes as a card, ring, key holder, wallet, smartphone sticky, and many more items for added convenience.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
Visit www.TheIdealCard.com to place your order for the only #Networking Card you'll ever need from just $15 ⁣@TheIdealCard⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
Developed by @INKGILITY, The World’s Most Innovative Marketing Company & Largest Selection of #BusinessCards @INKGILITY

node.text:
@waldanwatches is introducing the Heritage Professional “Pastel Edition” capsule collection. Limited to 300 pcs, each model is meticulously crafted with the modern watch wearer in mind and offers a more vibrant colorway into the Professional series with three different models, the ref. 0196BL (Sky Blue), ref. 0196P (Blush Pink) and ref. 0196C (Canary Yellow). 

Housed in their signature 40mm, 316L stainless steel case with a flat, anti-reflective treated sapphire crystal (5 ATM water resistant), these models are powered by the innovative and American Made “Ameriquartz” cal. 70200, which features jeweled bearings, is robustly machined of metal which makes them uniquely serviceable and carries a standard 5 year warranty. Each watch is complimented by genuine leather straps with “quick release” spring bars for easy changing and removal. Now available for pre-sale at waldanwatches.com.
